<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Github on Aurora</title><link>https://notes.yoooo.fun/tags/github/</link><description>Recent content in Github on Aurora</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Nov 2020 16:31:07 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://notes.yoooo.fun/tags/github/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to set schedule by github actions?</title><link>https://notes.yoooo.fun/posts/set-schedule4github-repo/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2020 21:58:58 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://notes.yoooo.fun/posts/set-schedule4github-repo/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="github-actions-schedule"&gt;Github Actions: Schedule
